 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EMayfair Gaming Group offers play-for-money mobile gaming across games of chance (casino/slots, etc) and skill (suduko, backgammon, etc), distributed via pubs in the United Kingdom.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThere are more than 60,000 pubs in the UK and most are screaming out for more revenue streams as operating margins dwindle due to factors such as the smoking ban, gaming limits on existing machines and consumer behavior.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EMayfair addresses this directly by providing pubs with a innovative revenue stream by providing patrons with a new alternative to traditional pub games.  Players purchase credits and download games that are played directly on their own mobile phone.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EPlayers top up their player account by purchasing credit vouchers in cash from the publican and redeem their winnings by either taking their mobile phone with a unique SMS code into any of the 14,000 post offices across the UK to redeem winnings up to 100 pounds or registering on a website and having payments made to their bank account.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EMayfair Mobile is the brand name of Mayfair Gaming Group Limited (Alderney, Channel Islands).\u003C/p\u003E",
